briefdescription.para: Function to handle set_vcurrent_velocity service. Sets the virtual currents velocity to the value requested by the service.
Function to handle reset_vcurrent service. Sets to the default values all variables used for simulating the virtual currents.

This function simulates the effect of currents in the measurements from the sensors. It takes in a dsor_msgs Measurement message and changes it or not depending on the effect of the set virtual current velocity.

This function publishes a State message for the console with the last measurements from the sensors. Its not filtered so its quite noisy, just used for reference on the real position of the vehicle when the filter is being changed with virtual currents.
